{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4e678001b5","title":"关于请班禅来京参加国庆问题的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"70ec0f8b7d","index":0,"year":1959,"month":9,"day":4,"articleId":"4e678001b5"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"e1d978187a","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"4e678001b5","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"班禅，即班禅额尔德尼·确吉坚赞，原西藏地方宗教和政治领袖之一。当时任全国人大常委会副委员长、西藏自治区筹备委员会代理主任委员。"},{"id":"39e4dd519d","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"4e678001b5","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中共西藏工委1959年8月29日关于班禅额尔德尼·确吉坚赞等在日喀则开展民主改革的一些情况给中央的报告上。"},{"id":"0fe027ff55","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"4e678001b5","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭真，当时任中共中央政治局委员、中央书记处书记。14]张国华，当时任中共西藏工委副书记、中国人民解放军西藏军区司今员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"feb9043ea3","type":"title","text":"关于请班禅来京参加国庆问题的批语？","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"4e678001b5"},{"id":"e1d978187a","type":"paragraph","text":"少奇、恩来、彭真同志","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"4e678001b5"},{"id":"39e4dd519d","type":"paragraph","text":"现离国庆只有二十几天了，宜劝班禅于九月十五日以前回拉萨，准备于九月二十日左右飞兰州，下句来京参加国庆。如何，请药定。张国华宜于九月十日以前返回拉萨。请彭找张谈一下，准备起程。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"4e678001b5"},{"id":"0fe027ff55","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"4e678001b5"},{"id":"d7a14a810b","type":"paragraph","text":"九月四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"4e678001b5"}],"page":{"id":"0febef204f","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"4e678001b5","start":340,"end":340}}}},"__N_SSG":true}